head_commit.message:
Implement Clone and Copy for PagingError

PagingError is a simple enum without associated data, so it can be
trivially cloned or copied.

head_commit.message:
Do not link to alloc crate

The alloc crate is not used anywhere in the codebase, so do not link to
it. This removes the requirement for downstream users to implement a
global allocator, which might not be possible.
